Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry to keep you waiting, sir. I'm ready now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Midori, taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kyouno...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who said we're attacking anybody?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? I just said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen... We can't just let you take it out for a flight whenever you feel like it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Besides, how do you expect to win when you don't even have a strategy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who makes the first move wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first rule of the Jersey Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get out of the cockpit and go on standby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now explain again from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if we don't get rid of all three Vox units,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll destroy them along with Pharos?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His objective is pretty clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of person are we dealing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sure is polite enough to declare war on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Debris?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Space trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More accurately, he's ex-royalty from a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that shared a longstanding alliance with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, currently he's the leader of a criminal group that calls itself "Kiss".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say he's the enemy mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How the mighty has fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said we have until daybreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my calculation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we only have about five hours left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say we comply with his demand and destroy all the Vox.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the enemy will leave Earth peacefully?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just be losing our only means of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost! This place is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Tadokoro! You need to hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami is my—!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"That's enough"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Watabe, please find us a marine location suitable for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll head there once all civilian personnel have been evacuated from this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,James, report the situation to every branch of the Foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coordinate with them to make absolutely sure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no ship or aircraft enters the airspace where the fighting will take place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uehara...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and complete final checks on both Vox units
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that Kyouno and Laffinty can fly at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Lan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this doesn't mean you may attack immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Dad's email said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this Villagiulio guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he bother to come all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's open it and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it. It hits the spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing your enemy begins from stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kirius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes pleasant and refreshing at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the moment it hits your stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this overpowering sweetness hits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This planet cannot be underestimated, Izo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're so dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty good, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did you go down there for, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two more hours 'til dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll find out then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest while you can or your body won't hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Energy is fully replenished!{The drink's name is Kamogawa Energy, btw}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she's all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, knowing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she won't let something like that get to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it would!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who wouldn't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone would react that way after being told such a horrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't use to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so noble, and caring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The past doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I don't know anything about that Giuvigiuvi guy's past!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... You're right, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I have every reason to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick his butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge up and let's go!{orig: Let's go fully charged!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wife... Well, she's my ex-wife now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She also had quite a sharp tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always let me have an earful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it hurts even now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,especially when I'm feeling lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But during times like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Novumundus Japan.
