Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here for Madoka, she already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I have some business with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enemy unit presence confirmed. All hands to battle stations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I repeat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enemy unit presence confirmed. All hands to battle stations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the enemy mother ship's position?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's matching our velocity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hovering above satellite tracking range.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why aren't they attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I ordered all non-combatant personnel off this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't mind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm related to that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Patch me through to the two pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's almost daybreak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The enemy is right above us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're practically sitting on top of us and we can't run nor hide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, what's wrong with Laffinty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems she drank too much Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to dilute that stuff before drinking it?{Undeniable evidence that Villagiulio and Madoka are related. All hail our Queen!}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember your previous battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Opening barrier walls numbers one and two.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pilot's heart rate, blood pressure, respiratory rate... all normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Opening the top hatch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A.I. Remote Systems are normal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All systems go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vox Aura, Vox Lympha, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orca! Taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not dawn yet, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Madoka!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple enemy Ovid launches confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number count...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two Vox crafts are about to make contact with the enemy units!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the weapon prototypes ready for launch, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Madoka and Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took off to get revenge for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, one shouldn't sympathize with the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after hearing your story,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even I felt like punching that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly a terrible man, that Villagiulio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A subordinate risks her life to sneak behind enemy lines
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and manages to steal their treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet he shows no remorse in discarding her, simply because she acted against his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he was aware of your sincere feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How ungrateful of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.83,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he realize that not everyone can achieve Memoria?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have some neat stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be careful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! There's no end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help is on its way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:14:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:14:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone in Ignis's cockpit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it up on the monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's already entered the T.O. sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't stop me now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will really, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know when to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignis's Vox System has been activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer control it with the A.I. Remote!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find her to be quite gifted, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can scold me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you find so amusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, if this means good-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well... I'll just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she planning to go in alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You boys stand by here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning to take on those three by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harem night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wait. It's almost morning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's another manned enemy craft!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henceforth, it will be identified as enemy unit four!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be the one that appeared in Kamogawa last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giuvigiubaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my fault for acting on my own{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}without ever taking Brother's feelings into account!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brother isn't to blame!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stupid girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you still defending him after what he said to you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should dump someone like him.{CHAR KICK!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.22,0:19:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You haven't considered my feelings in the least!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one asked you to get revenge for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You talk big about wanting to help other people,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but the Jersey Club and everything you do...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only doing it for your own selfish reasons!
