Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My jersey is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the washing machine?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not there. Maybe someone stole it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muginami?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.63,0:23:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.47,0:23:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't steal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now, Lan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't take it. I just tried it on, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.76,0:23:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was really tight around my chest...
